      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCbe4dc47824f1100583a1b051d7198fd2"></a>Installation of the engine
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10601"> </a>Refitting is the reverse of removal.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10604"> </a>Apply the specified grease and tighten nuts (1) to a torque of 60 Nm ± 5% on pins (2) and (3).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10607"> </a>Apply the specified grease and tighten screws (5) to a torque of 72 Nm ± 5%.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10609"> </a>Apply recommended threadlocker and tighten screws (4) to a torque of 42 Nm ± 5%.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10611"> </a>Refit the removed parts by performing the steps shown in the table and in the specific sections of the manual in reverse order.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_058602989.jpg"></center>
      </div>
