      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10622"> </a>If previously removed, refit the frame lateral plates (<a href="80877.html#DUC914159e82b7410058b64bff18abbeac4">Refitting the lateral plates</a>), after having properly installed the shims (<a href="80873.html#DUC953d28382b7410058b64bff18abbeac4">Refitting structural components</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10631"> </a>Connect wiring connectors on the engine block.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10633"> </a>Refit the side stand (<a href="80856.html#DUC871b7f202b7410058b64bff18abbeac4">Refitting the side stand</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10638"> </a>Refit the central stand, if any (<a href="80860.html#DUCa72a7f502b7410058b64bff18abbeac4">Refitting the central stand</a>)
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10643"> </a>Refit the front sprocket (<a href="79976.html#DUC6a6ab4402b2410058de4ee3905e05ec4">Refitting the front sprocket</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10648"> </a>Refit the clutch slave cylinder (<a href="78740.html#DUC1fe52c982b2410058cedd30e2bfae6c4">Refitting the clutch slave cylinder</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10653"> </a>Refit the gearchange control (<a href="78753.html#DUC3bd7a8f02b37100580b28b55a208bfd2">Refitting the gearchange control</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10658"> </a>Connect the solenoid starter/starter motor cable (<a href="45213.html#DUCc8b137a826841005887ee38e40fd97d2">Refitting the starter motor</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10663"> </a>Refit the water radiator lower fastener on the engine (<a href="44922.html#DUC8e956eb0250110058a828a10427928d2">Refitting the water radiator</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10668"> </a>Refit the cooling system hoses and unions on the engine block (<a href="44926.html#DUC62ddf200250210058a868a10427928d2">Refitting the cooling system hoses and unions</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10673"> </a>Refill the cooling system (<a href="77257.html#DUCf34a5aa829f91005800d816ce97b3fd2">Changing the coolant</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10678"> </a>Refit the cooler oil hoses on the engine block (<a href="44910.html#DUC354498d024f3100583a9b051d7198fd2">Refitting the lubrication system</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10684"> </a>Fill the lubrication system (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10689"> </a>Refit the exhaust system (<a href="79886.html#DUC3c9607002b2310058d62a5fdf30dcfc4">Refitting the exhaust system</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10694"> </a>Connect the cap cables to the spark plugs.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10696"> </a>Refit the filter box, the throttle body, the blow-by and the oil breather pipe (<a href="79872.html#DUC528844882b2310058d68a5fdf30dcfc4">Refitting filter box and throttle body</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10701"> </a>Refit the secondary air system valve and pipes (<a href="79880.html#DUC435821402b2310058d66a5fdf30dcfc4">Refitting the secondary air system</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10706"> </a>Connect the throttle control cable (<a href="78731.html#DUC075b1ad02b23100589efb93796bc81c4">Refitting the throttle control</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10711"> </a>Refit the air filter (<a href="79876.html#DUC556760082b2310058d68a5fdf30dcfc4">Refitting the air filters</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10716"> </a>Refit the fuel tank (Refitting the fuel tank<a href="79868.html#DUC4f6912c82b2310058d68a5fdf30dcfc4"></a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10720"> </a>Refit the instrument panel internal covers (<a href="77977.html#DUC2fbfd0b02a74100585b5e07f17a720d2">Refitting the panel</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10725"> </a>Refit the oil sump guard unit (<a href="78008.html#DUC69eeed302aaa10058bbcf20939ae18d2">Refitting the oil sump guard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10730"> </a>Refit the half-fairings (<a href="77989.html#DUCad6937a02a961005810acc3160c450d2">Refitting the tank fairings</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10736"> </a>Refit the front half-fairings (<a href="77985.html#DUC1ccd37182a8810058cfc8ef6d8d608d2">Refitting the front half-fairing</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10741"> </a>Refit the side body panels (<a href="77995.html#DUC521908882a9810058110cc3160c450d2">Refitting side body panels and tail guard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10746"> </a>Refit the seats (<a href="77997.html#DUC853ddbd82a9a10058426b9f0263a2cd2">Refitting the seat</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
